 the film,” he continued. “I was so honoured to work with him.我从他那里学到了很多东西，整个演员除了对他和船员的爱和尊重外，什么都没有。 That&#39;s the experience I had in the making of this film, and that&#39;s the truth of what our filmmaking was on set.” </p><figure id="attachment_3837344" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837344" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837344" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Anthony-Mackie-Harrison-Ford.jpg" alt="美国队长：勇敢的新世界" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Anthony-Mackie-Harrison-Ford.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Anthony-Mackie-Harrison-Ford-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Anthony-Mackie-Harrison-Ford-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Anthony-Mackie-Harrison-Ford-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Anthony-Mackie-Harrison-Ford-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Anthony-Mackie-Harrison-Ford-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837344" class="wp-caption-text"> Athony Mackie and Harrison Ford. CREDIT: Michael Buckner/Variety via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> In <em>Captain America: Brave New World</em> , Ford replaces the late William Hurt, who originated the role of Thaddeus “Thunderbolt” Ross in 2008&#39;s <em>The Incredible Hulk</em> .</p><p> Elsewhere in the <em>Variety</em> interview, Onah spoke about working with Ford on Thaddeus&#39; panic attack scenes, and how the actor threw himself into the role.</p><p> “Harrison is so committed,” said the director. “I went to his house very early on in the process, and we talked quite a great deal about what it would mean to have Thaddeus Ross backslide into who he used to be.</p><p> “We meet him in the beginning of the movie, and you imagine this is guy who&#39;s wizened and mellowed out.然后思考这种脾气，这种愤怒，因为事情不断挫败他的计划，以制定该条约，以公平地分发全球的金刚裔。他必须开始失去控制。</p><p> “We talked about what the physicality of that would look like, how that rage would emanate. Harrison, what&#39;s great about him is you have these conversations, and then he finds it in the moment, in the scene, what feels organic when he&#39;s in that space. So it was prep and then trusting the man — of course, how can you not trust Harrison Ford?”</p><p> In a <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/captain-america-brave-new-world-review-anthony-mackie-marvel-3837635">two-star review</a> of <em>Brave New World</em> , <em>NME</em> wrote: “With footage looking murky, from the opening chapel-set shoot-out onwards, <em>Brave New World</em> lacks the gleaming beauty of the best MCU films… This is a functional Marvel movie that offers little excitement.一场激烈的诉讼程序，其中包括一条衬有樱花树的道路上的诉讼。但这在很大程度上是沉闷而令人失望的。”</p><p> In other Marvel news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/paul-rudd-reveals-his-two-favourite-marvel-movies-3840338">Paul Rudd recently revealed which two movies from the MCU are his favourites</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/captain-america-brave-new-world-director-denies-harrison-ford-diva-accusations-he-was-an-utter-professional-3840367">&#39;Captain America: Brave New World&#39; director denies Harrison Ford “diva” accusations: “He was an utter professional”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
